The Syntel Story
Since 1980, Syntel has invested in IP, solutions and world-class talent to enable our clients to thrive and grow in an evolving business world. Learn more about us and how we do it.




Pioneering Spirit  Syntel opened its first India development center in 1992, becoming one of the first U.S. companies to employ the Global Delivery Model.

 



U.S. Owned and Operated Syntel has been publicly-traded on Nasdaq since 1997, trading under the ticker symbol SYNT.

 



Global Reach Syntel delivers services from 3 continents, with development centers in India, the U.S., Scotland, Poland and the Philippines.

 



Commitment to Diversity Syntel is a certified Minority-owned Business (MBE) and is committed to gender diversity and building a vibrant, inclusive work culture.

 

